  "system": {
    "description": "<p><strong>Not from the PDF's Example Starships stat blocks</strong> -- only the large-station hull row (Building a Starship, hull table) and a one-paragraph blurb exist in the source; this loadout is an original example built on that hull for this pack. A station has no Speed and no spike drive, and cannot maneuver in combat. The Arx is a major trade hub for a wealthy world, with enough point defenses and boarding countermeasures to deter pirates and smugglers drawn to its traffic.</p><p><strong>Cargo:</strong> 5,000 tons (informational estimate). <strong>Cost:</strong> 40M base price (hull table).</p>",
